  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca \u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Interruption to train services",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Gamini Seneviratne, Deputy General Manager (Transport) of the Railways says that more trains may be canceled in the coming days due to the shortage of staff due to the lack of fuel to reach the workplace.",
        "He further said that due to fuel shortage, many trains had to be canceled today (29) and the situation could worsen in the coming days."
      ],
